title: The Complete Handgun 1300 to the Present - Ivan V Hogg - 1979.pd
description: PDF.114 pages. Text replaced, bookmarks. Fully searchable. Paragraphs moved together. Unfortunately this book has some pictures that are spread across two pages, so there is a gap in the pictures where the centre of the pages are. I have used the pictures that were on one page, and where possible replaced split pictures, for the others I have patched the pictures together but this obviously leaves a gap.
